::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe stops in time to avoid Steel, the kick from Brooder sending him 
flying forward. He growls.

"Jets."

The sides of his torso open, two jets emerging. He takes off into the air, 
going as fast as he can. He hoped these two wouldn't follow him, or he could 
be in trouble.
